#Worldpeace or peace on #Earth is an ideal state of #freedom, #peace, and #happiness among and within all #nations and #people. This ideal of world non-violence provides a basis for peoples and nations to willingly cooperate, #either #voluntarily or by virtue of a system of governance that prevents warfare. While different cultures, religions, philosophies, and #organizations may have differing concepts about how such an ideal state might come about, they have in common this ideal of a cessation of all hostility amongst all #humanity.

#World Peace could be established through religious or secular organizations that address to #human rights, #technology, #education, #engineering, medicine, or diplomacy used as an end to all forms of fighting. For #example, since 1945, the #UnitedNations and the 5 permanent members of its #Security Council (the #US, #Russia, #China, #France, and the UK) have worked to resolve conflicts without #war or declarations of war. However, #nations have entered numerous military conflicts since that #time.

Former US Secretary of State and unsuccessful presidential candidate Hillary Clinton has officially launched her new political organization, called 'Onward Together'.
The organization will support various Democratic and progressive movements, groups and candidates in the future.
Some weeks ago Clinton officially announced herself as part of the resistance against US President Donald Trump, now she officially announced her comeback on the political stage.
Clinton said that Americans "are speaking out like never before" and that she believes "more fiercely than ever" that American citizens need to "engage at every level" to keep American democracy "strong and vibrant."
Clinton added that while the past year hasn't been what she envisioned, she will continue "fighting for a kinder, big-hearted, inclusive America."
/
Clinton's new organization will financially support all groups and political candidates that promote Democratic and progressive agendas. 
The groups that Clinton and Onward Together will initially support are:
⚊
- Swing Left
An organization founded by the US Democratic Party with the goal to take back the majority in Congress in the midterm elections in 2018.
⚊
- Indivisible Team
A group of former US Congress staffers who help people get in contact with their representatives to have their voices heard.
⚊
- Color of Change
An organization with the goal to reform the American justice system and end racial discrimination.
⚊
- Emerge America
An organization that encourages and supports Democratic women to run for political offices.
⚊
- Run for Something
An organization that encourages and supports young Democrats to run for political offices.
/
Onward Together announced that a lot more Leftist groups and organizations will be supported in the near future.
.
